@startuml
title Dis Klinigi - Kullanici Girisi ve Oturum Dogrulamasi

actor "Klinik Personeli" as Staff
boundary "LoginPage (UI)" as LoginUI
boundary "api.ts Auth Service" as ApiService
control "TokenObtainPairView" as TokenView
control "CurrentUserView" as MeView
entity "CustomUser" as User
database "JWT Storage\n(localStorage)" as JwtStore

Staff -> LoginUI : kullaniciAdi/sifre gir
LoginUI -> ApiService : login(username,password)
ApiService -> TokenView : POST /api/auth/token/
TokenView -> User : kimlik bilgisi dogrula
User --> TokenView : dogrulama sonucu
TokenView --> ApiService : access, refresh token
ApiService -> JwtStore : setTokens(access,refresh)
ApiService --> LoginUI : login basarili

LoginUI -> ApiService : fetchCurrentUser()
ApiService -> MeView : GET /api/auth/me/ (Bearer access)
MeView -> User : request.user bilgisini al
User --> MeView : id, ad, rol
MeView --> ApiService : kullanici profili
ApiService --> LoginUI : ekrani role gore ac

@enduml
